property.value:
This Co-Simulation Bouncing Ball FMI-2.0 FMU is from FMUSDK.
The stop time (4.0) and period (aka step) (0.01) are from fmusdk2.0.3/run_all.bat
The fmu sets the initial values: h=1, v=0
During initialization: der(h) = -g, where g = 9.81
During event update, if the height (h) is > 0: v = - e * v, where e = 0.7
